Amazing Project by @faroukabououf
AAST Alexandria, Egypt

Via @wisearchitecture

The PSYCHIATRIC HEALTH RESORT is an all-inclusive psychiatric hospital. The experienced staff, facilities, individualized, and group services provide a safe and therapeutic environment for those suffering from psychological problems.

The project aim is to serve the country and specifically Alexandria by offering a new, much needed service and bring more focus and awareness to Mental and Physical Health. “Care, Science and Quality”  We aim at promoting Mental Health and providing state of the art management of psychiatric disorders using Nature and green elements..
